			<script type="application/json" data-sveltekit-fetched data-url="https://api.printables.com/graphql/" data-hash="1gb3iem">{"status":200,"statusText":"OK","headers":{"content-type":"application/json"},"body":"{\"data\":{\"contests\":[{\"id\":\"500\",\"slug\":\"upcycling-new-prusament-spools\",\"name\":\"Upcycling NEW Prusament Spools\",\"teaserImageFilePath\":\"media/competition/teaser_images/None/small_banner.jpg\",\"description\":\"### **\\ud83c\\udfc1 Starting:  April 02, 2026, Ending: May 02, 2026 23:59 UTC.**\\r\\n\\r\\n### **\\ud83d\\udcc5 Entries: from October 01, 2025 to May 02, 2026 23:59 UTC.**\\r\\n\u003Cbr>\\r\\n\\r\\n### Give the new Prusament spool a second life!\\r\\nA few years ago, we ran a Printables contest focused on reusing the old Prusament spools, and the results were full of great ideas. With the [new Prusament spool](https://www.prusa3d.com/downloads/press/prusament-portfolio-november-2025.pdf), it\\u2019s a good time to return to this theme! Upcycle the spool in any way you like and give it a new purpose! A spool can become a stand, a small table, a hanger, a workshop helper, a piece of art, or something entirely different. \\r\\n\\r\\nIf you haven\\u2019t had a chance to get your hands on new spool yet, don't worry, you can download a [dummy model of the spool on Printables](https://www.printables.com/model/1648762-dummy-prusament-spool-for-makers).\\r\\n\\r\\n#### We have two simple rules:\\r\\n* First, we know there are many different spool types, but for this contest, we\\u2019re focusing on new Prusament spools only. \\r\\n* Second, your project should reuse the actual spool (or its parts) itself as part of the final build.\\r\\n\u003Cbr>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nTo help you start, we\\u2019re bringing you a selection of some nice Prusament spool upcycling projects from Printables in the contest article. Just hit the \\\"Entry info\\\" button. \\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n### \\ud83d\\udcf8\\u2b50 Hero model of this contest: [Prusament Spool Lamp](https://www.printables.com/model/685180-prusament-spool-lamp)\",\"isOpen\":true,\"openFrom\":\"2026-04-02T08:39:19+00:00\",\"openTo\":\"2026-05-02T22:59:00+00:00\",\"modelsCount\":65,\"winnerPrize\":\"\u003Ca href=\\\"https://www.prusa3d.com/product/prusa-core-one-kit/\\\">Prusa CORE One+ kit\u003C/a> and more than 5600 Prusameters in total!\",\"entryLink\":\"https://blog.prusa3d.com/\",\"winnersLink\":\"\",\"printDateValidation\":\"2025-10-01T00:00:00+00:00\",\"signedModelsCount\":null,\"maxModelsPerUser\":5,\"aiGeneratedPrintsDisabled\":true,\"__typename\":\"CompetitionType\"},{\"id\":\"508\",\"slug\":\"armrest-tables\",\"name\":\"Armrest Tables\",\"teaserImageFilePath\":\"media/competition/teaser_images/None/small_banner_couches.jpg\",\"description\":\"### **\\ud83c\\udfc1 Starting: April 03, 2026, Ending: April 19, 2026 23:59 UTC.**\\r\\n\\r\\n### **\\ud83d\\udcc5 Entries: from March 01, 2026 to April 19, 2026 23:59 UTC.**\\r\\n\u003Cbr>Every couch is a center of relaxation, so it makes sense to have simple solutions that keep everything close at hand without taking up too much space. The armrest tables theme includes all kinds of useful accessories, from basic trays to holders for drinks, remotes, books, or snacks. Create practical, stable, and easy-to-use designs for a comfy couch environment! If it stands on its own, hangs, slides between cushions, or works in another smart way, it counts.\\r\\n\u003Cbr>\\r\\n\u003Cbr>\\r\\n### \\ud83d\\udcf8\\u2b50 Hero model of this contest: [Couch armrest table](https://www.printables.com/model/1268295-bouquet-of-easter-daffodils)\",\"isOpen\":true,\"openFrom\":\"2026-04-03T11:09:02+00:00\",\"openTo\":\"2026-04-19T22:59:00+00:00\",\"modelsCount\":45,\"winnerPrize\":\"\u003Ca href=\\\"https://www.printables.com/prusameter\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">500 Prusameters\u003C/a> which are more than enough for one Prusament spool. The winner will also receive the Printables honorary badge, and up to 900 Prusameters will be distributed among other top entries.\",\"entryLink\":\"\",\"winnersLink\":\"\",\"printDateValidation\":\"2026-03-01T00:00:00+00:00\",\"signedModelsCount\":null,\"maxModelsPerUser\":5,\"aiGeneratedPrintsDisabled\":true,\"__typename\":\"CompetitionType\"}]}}"}</script>
